4.plot: Another day at the office just turned into a fight for survival. How resilient are you? Do you need to toughen up? Five inner city recruitment agents are about to discover the true meaning of a cutthroat environment.

imdb.plot outline: Each week Do or Die drops a group of unsuspecting workers into some of the harshest Australian environments for five gruelling days. Calling on the help of workplace psychologist and outdoor adventurer, Dr Travis Kemp, the group is sent on what they believe to be a fun team-building exercise. Instead, they'll be flung into a survival adventure with no escape. It's Do or Die! A week full of emotional highs and lows, dramatic twists and turns, bringing the participants to the edge as they grapple with their own limitations, and the limitations of their colleagues. Can they survive not only the adventure, but also each other?! Will they make it back to the office inspired, motivated and ready for change? Do or Die is one hour of adventure, conflict and drama played out against the stunning backdrop of Australia's wilderness. Can office politics be put aside when the boss is dangling off a cliff? Would you put your life in the hands of the office bully?
imdb.title: Do or Die
plot: _Do or Die_ (qv) is a series where regular office workers are thrown into a survival adventure that will change their lives and workplaces forever.::ABC
